/////////
> Es5
(Ecma Script)
> Es6

//es5
function add(a,b){
    return a+b
}

//es6
const add = (a,b) =>  {return a+b}


Local Dependency
> Local to the folder
> Can be used in same folder only
> npm i packagename

Dev dependency
> Just like normal dependency
> Only use at the time development
> npm i --save-dev packagename


Global Dependency
> Installed in the system
> No Specific folder
> Need admin permissions to install
> Mainly use for Start build the app
> Not added to package.json

# window
> open cmd as admin
> npm i -g packagename

# Mac/linuc
> Open terminal
> sudo npm i -g packagename
** Nodemon
> npm i -g nodemon



